{"tid":1778814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"返校有人搞包場","createTime":"2019-12-11T08:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T17:52:19.000Z","uid":268230,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"500468b7dbe6418fe30fe4cf04f4216f8d8882a9","tid":1778814,"uid":268230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/289306124578369/posts/1417415695100734?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F289306124578369%2Fposts%2F1417415695100734%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a51b15c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/289306124578369/posts/1417415695100734?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少手足因今次「返送中」抗爭而出現經濟困難，希望透過今次包場活動，除了大家可以欣賞一套「致自由」的電影外，亦可以幫助手足，舒緩他們的經濟壓力，希望大家可以慷慨解囊，多多支持￼！￼<br />\n<br />\n金金在此拜謝各位香港人！<br />\n<br />\n「返校」<br />\n<br />\n日期：22-Dec -2019 <br />\n時間：19:30 <br />\n地點：UA MegaBox -House 5<br />\n票價：HK$200位（戲票實價$85位） <br />\n可容納人數 ：90人 （不設劃位）<br />\n<br />\n扣減票價剩下餘額全部捐給支援手足生活的組織：學聯抗爭支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n請大家先付款然後inbox你的稱呼、聯絡方式、認購了幾多張戲票、以及過數紙（或Cap過數圖）給金金作實，戲票將於當日在放影前半小時在戲院門口派發。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家捐助多些，令更多手足受惠，或捐助後轉贈戲票給義士去觀賞。<br />\n<br />\n銀行轉帳 - 滙豐銀行：614-079879-833 (LEUNG KAM SHING C R)<br />\n轉數快 - 9152 1807<br />\n<br />\n下面是介紹「學聯抗爭支援基金」運作以及他們的眾籌Post:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/269056797871/posts/10156913487302872/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F269056797871%2Fposts%2F10156913487302872%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=531c142a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/269056797871/posts/10156913487302872/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/269056797871/posts/10156924826202872/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F269056797871%2Fposts%2F10156924826202872%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=74a299bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/269056797871/posts/10156924826202872/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#返校 #自由 #政治打壓 #白色恐怖 #香港人 #學聯抗爭支援基金"},{"pid":"c9f69ecc1d6beb582053bed3ed4831c830c3e146","tid":1778814,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"咁都有得抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33a713bce97b9d67c0fc2e205b2c1366e74a7d9","tid":1778814,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"ee55d9f9ec5ccdee7d62495d194074ab14cf1197","tid":1778814,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"間野醒喎<br />\n原來人人85蚊睇<br />\n之後115蚊可以捐俾其他基金<br />\n<br />\n而家一炮過攬住黎食"},{"pid":"7adee58c044a1a91589938121a9d328f09e15d54","tid":1778814,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"唔明點解MegaBox間有得播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed89c8c2cd7c3e386f588f72d03223e13bb5e9bc","tid":1778814,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3479f8247b38c841ba901200562d81b28e9c402b","tid":1778814,"uid":282452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"22號要食冬至飯不了"},{"pid":"7bd7ff8e282cdf3a7a04afd4344f9d2695e6ae4b","tid":1778814,"uid":335708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl